<div class="chapter">
<div class="titlepage"><div><div><h1 class="title">
<a id="id1340"></a>Chapter 1. XMLStarlet Example</h1></div></div></div>
<p>The <span class="emphasis"><em>XMLStarlet</em></span> command line toolkit
  allows querying/checking/editing/transforming/formatting XML documents
  from command line</p>
<p>To find out more on how to use the
  <span class="emphasis"><em>XMLStarlet</em></span> for XML processing, point
  your browser to <a class="ulink" href="http://xmlstar.sourceforge.net/" target="_top">http://xmlstar.sourceforge.net/</a>.
  </p>
